methods.computeRedirections:
Stamps the left-hand-side values with the corresponding right hand side.

 The rightKeyIndices are parallel to the stamp values in rightStamps; and used to compute a new chunk of
 redirections parallel to leftStamps.

:param leftStamps: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.Chunk<io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Values>) - the input lhs stamp values
:param rightStamps: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.Chunk<io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Values>) - the input rhs stamp values
:param rightKeyIndices: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.LongChunk<io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.RowKeys>) - the input rhs stamp indices
:param leftRedirections: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.WritableLongChunk<io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.RowKeys>) - the resulting redirections from the stamping operation
